{"tid":1849074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[[忽發奇想]] 如何將「黑警死全家」付諸實行讓病毒和黑警connect！","createTime":"2020-01-28T23:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T02:26:15.000Z","uid":292343,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f3f9dc67333714bbf699b246ae1f89e99505d6","tid":1849074,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T23:21:31.000Z","msg":"「黑警死全家」不再是口號<br />\n<br />\n信封 或者 公文袋<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好放啲用過嘅口罩入去<br />\n(如果唔想佢哋摸到質感而唔開)<br />\n或者可以<br />\n求其放啲寫字用嘅紙入去<br />\n放入去之前千祈唔好喺上面咳<br />\n或者沾啲病毒上去<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">然後千祈唔好寄去黑警屋企</span></strong><br />\n千祈唔好上老豆搵仔搵地址寄<br />\n<br />\n(1. 唔好放自己用過嘅口罩)<br />\n(2. 處理成件事要好小心唔好比自己接觸觸摸到病毒<br />\n或者喺紙張/信封留低指紋)<br />\n<br />\n或者任何其他可以沾有病毒嘅媒介 or 物件<br />\n都記住千祈唔好寄去黑警屋企<br />\n如果黑警屋企不幸染病<br />\n唔只會死全家<br />\n仲會返狗屋傳染比其他狗<br />\n千祈千祈唔好咁樣做<br />\n<br />\n有咩補充 歡迎一齊討論"},{"pid":"2fca7508027d09fc6b0047600e83b33ab30bbc9e","tid":1849074,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T23:22:09.000Z","msg":"p牌都自推10次"},{"pid":"a44e7141ae78d67aa488ff446efd1c8a3f0923e3","tid":1849074,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T23:22:20.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5d8edc25db879f64368e3d33766e33d6731a548f","tid":1849074,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T23:22:30.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"313e69fcdb3b789d611f3545c0032c7342994860","tid":1849074,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T23:23:02.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8180e1783c11099a46cc6e4082cea6a138da6a64","tid":1849074,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T23:23:14.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"65dcd38681910f4498449709f29464771fbd4fdb","tid":1849074,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T23:23:26.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"339f5c0019a1aff6b7e0b8daacbb0c12e2bcef8e","tid":1849074,"uid":2923